Terminating Turmites
--------------------

Build using CMake (www.cmake.org).

Build on Linux:

> mkdir build
> cd build
> ccmake ..
(configure, generate)
> make

Build on Windows:

1) Run the CMake GUI.
2) Specify a separate build directory.
3) Specify the IDE you want to target.
4) Configure, generate.
5) Compile in your chosen IDE.

Contact: tim.hutton@gmail.com
